result.execSummary:
The defendant Tyrese T Williams was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Tyrese T Williams is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Tyrese T Williams was found guilty of Battery [Modifiers: Repeater], a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.19(1).
